  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RouterNavigator<StateT extends RouterNavigatorState>
    Simple utility for switching a child router based on a state.
    RouterNavigator.AttachTransition<RouterT extends com.uber.rib.core.Router,StateT extends RouterNavigatorState>
    Allows consumers to write custom attachment logic when switching states.
    RouterNavigator.DetachTransition<RouterT extends com.uber.rib.core.Router,StateT extends RouterNavigatorState>
    Allows consumers to write custom detachment logic wen switching states.
    RouterNavigatorFactory.Strategy
    Strategy to employ when using this factory to generate new RouterNavigators.
    RouterNavigatorState
    Represents states for ModernRouterNavigator.
  • Class Summary
